Package: z-push
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, php5, php5-cli, libapache2-mod-php5, php5-xsl, php5-curl, php5-ldap, php5-imap, php-mail, libawl-php, dialog, gzip
Conflicts: sogo-activesync
Description: an implementation of the ActiveSync protocol
 Z-push is an implementation of the ActiveSync protocol which is used
 'over-the-air' for multi platform ActiveSync devices, including Android,
 Windows Mobile, iPhone, Sony Ericsson and Nokia mobile devices. With
 Z-push any groupware can be connected and synced with these devices.
